<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Commendation" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Commendation,</orth> 1) recommendation: <cit><quote>the gentleman is come to me, with c. from great potentates,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tgv 2.4.79" default="NO" valid="yes">Gentl. II, 4, 79</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the c. is not in his wit, but in his villuny,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ado 2.1.145" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado II, 1, 145</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. aww 2.2.70" default="NO" valid="yes">All's II, 2, 70</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. aww 4.3.92" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 3, 92</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 3.2.40" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. III, 2, 40</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 1.4.166" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. I, 4, 166</bibl>.<lb />2) greeting: <cit><quote>a word or two of --s sent from Valentine,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tgv 1.3.53" default="NO" valid="yes">Gentl. I, 3, 53</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 2.2.99" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. II, 2, 99</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 2.181" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL II, 181</bibl> <cit><quote>(do).</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 5.3.176" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A V, 3, 176</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. h8 4.2.118" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 IV, 2, 118</bibl>.
<lb />3) praise: <cit><quote>only this c. I can afford her,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ado 1.1.175" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado I, 1, 175</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>shall turn all into my --s,</quote> <bibl n="shak. cym 4.1.23" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. IV, 1, 23</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. mv 4.1.166" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. IV, 1, 166</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 1.2.275" default="NO" valid="yes">As I, 2, 275</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. aww 1.1.49" default="NO" valid="yes">All's I, 1, 49</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. aww 1.1.49" default="NO" valid="yes">All's I, 1, 49</bibl> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 3.1.189" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A III, 1, 189</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 5.3.122" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 V, 3, 122</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tim 1.1.166" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. I, 1, 166</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 1.4.55" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. I, 4, 55</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. per 2.2.9" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. II, 2, 9</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>